data.Name: nothing less
data.Bio: High energy, catchy hooks and a solid stage show are just a few things Nothing Less fans have come to expect. Over the last five years their sound has developed and matured into their brand of unique, guitar-driven, lyrically intense, hook-laced punk-rock that will have you singing along within seconds. Nothing Less is no stranger to the music scene. The band has released three full-length albums, lived in three different states (including Alaska) Read more on Last.fm
